Clenchedfist is an early stage, open source, retro style racing game engine, written in blitz3d. 0.1 version features:
Visual:     
    -low polycount, NFS 6 graphic style,
    -dynamic shadows,
    -static lightning,
    -bumpmapping,
    -animated skybox,
    -reflections,
    -pfx, fog, blur,
Mechanics:
    Arcade driving style with implemented:
        -acceleration, velocity,
        -frond/rear wheel drive,
        -air resistance, braking, weight transfer
        -slip ratio, traction force,
        -low, high speed turning
        -all variables placed in script file, regardless from the engine code
        
